  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.9.5">
<l>miṉṉaṉaiya nuṇmaruṅkul melliyaṟkā yilaṅkai vēntaṉmuṭi yorupatuntō ḷirupatumpō yutira</l>
<l>taṉnikaril cilaivaḷaittaṉ ṟilaṅkaipoṭi ceyta taṭantōḷaṉ makiḻntiṉitu maruviyuṟai kōyil</l>
<l>cenneloṭu ceṅkamalañ cēlkayalkaḷ vāḷai ceṅkaḻunī roṭumiṭaintu kaḻaṉitikaḻn teṅkum</l>
<l>maṉṉupukaḻ vētiyarkaḷ maliveytu nāṅkūr vaikunta viṇṇakaram vaṇaṅkumaṭa neñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Simple heart, worship in Vaikunta Viṇṇakaram in Nānkūr which acquires</l>
<l rend="indent">the best of Vedic experts of eternal fame,</l>
<l>Where the fields glitter everywhere, being crowded with red paddy,</l>
<l rend="indent">red lotuses, carp, kayal and vāḷai [fish], and red waterlilies,</l>
<l>The temple where dwells the broad-shouldered one,</l>
<l rend="indent">happily with affection [and] rejoicing, who, bending his incomparable bow</l>
<l>So the ten crowns and twenty arms of Lanka’s king went tumbling,</l>
<l rend="indent">for the sake of the tender one, her thin waist like lightning,</l>
<l rend="indent">made ash of Lanka that day.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
